曾因名誉权纠纷被蔚来控股有限公司起诉。 值得一提的是，去年，顾宇波曾因买卖合同纠纷起诉蔚来控股有限公司、蔚来汽车销售服务有限公司、徐州蔚来汽车销售服务有限公司。 据媒体报道，顾宇波曾发视频称，他已将蔚来告上法庭，理由是他全款购买蔚来 ES6，但蔚来拒绝交付。蔚来法务部回应称，鉴于顾宇波对蔚来及用户进行谩骂、污蔑和攻击，蔚来已通知解除汽车购买协议，拒绝向其出售蔚来品牌车辆，并于解约当天退还全部款项、支付协议内涉及的双倍车辆定金。 2023 年 11 月 6 日，蔚来法务部发布声明称，蔚来诉抖音账号「小牛说车」名誉侵权案一审宣判，「小牛说车」被判赔偿 60 余万元、致歉 90 天。彻底凉凉！500 万粉丝网红，账号被封禁！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2486150e12d1971c7aa6bd9cc23b621f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658385839"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI1uvWhbPNiI0OEAMaCTEwODU4NTk0OSDogI+zBjAAOOkDQBRyCTY1ODM4NTgzOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1717906976.853098", "card_id": "Q_655250450", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 493}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "能分享一下你最近的人生感悟吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-614a01a7d32672ed500f60c17f4cd92e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "48 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655250450"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI1uvWhbPNiI0OEAMaCTEwNzg4ODc2NiDK+OexBjAAOLIEQBVyCTY1NTI1MDQ1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1717906976.856725", "card_id": "Q_655505386", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 156}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很多高学历人才也不能脱离低级趣味？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5bd84670d39ae3ef02210aa8716d966c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": 